                            <comment id="56805" author="simmonsja" created="Tue, 23 Apr 2013 13:26:59 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For the last test shot we did not get a lock up so that is the good news. It did take 5 minutes to unmount the MGT but it is not a show stopper for us.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="55764" author="simmonsja" created="Mon, 8 Apr 2013 17:30:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I figure the reason for this was that it only occurs are very large scale so it doesn&apos;t impact every one. Now it would be nice to see this fixed before the release &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/smile.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; I have a test shot this week end coming up so we can see if the problem still exist and if it does we can get a crash dump this time.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="55757" author="bfaccini" created="Mon, 8 Apr 2013 15:48:27 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;James, Do you agree that we can reduce ticket&apos;s priority to Major ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54555" author="simmonsja" created="Thu, 21 Mar 2013 12:13:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have bad news. The admin never got a crash dump &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; We are going to have to reproduce it at a smaller scale.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54421" author="bfaccini" created="Tue, 19 Mar 2013 20:31:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;No problem James.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="54408" author="simmonsja" created="Tue, 19 Mar 2013 19:12:38 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Sure as soon as admin comes in tomorrow I will get the proper core dump. Sorry about that.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
